Question 5️⃣ (Very Common Interview Question)

Create a POST API in Spring Boot to add a new student.

Endpoint
POST /student
Request Body
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Ravi",
  "course": "Java"
}
Requirement

Use @RequestBody
-----
@RestController
public class StudentController{
    @Autowired
    private StudentService ss;
    @PostMapping("/student")
    public Student saveStudent(@RequestBody Student student)
    {
        return ss.save(student);
    }
}
